Map created for Gaming Portal www.TWSE.cz

Contains:

- 6 spawnpoints for CT and 18 for Terrorist - One hidden shaft in the cell - Fully functional soccer area - Pool - Minigames with deagle - Chicken and knife fight arena (ring - raw vs. smeckdown) + hell in the cell - Aim arena with 3x m4a1,ak47, desert deagle and he grenade + hiden awp and flashbang - Chasm for roulette - Epic credits Thanks for download and sorry for my english.

Have a FUN!
